metadata.name: Through the clouds
metadata.description:
This is one of the rearest seeings and one of my most viral photos i have posted so far.  Even Nato contacted me same day i posted it.  I took this photo from my house when this huge aircraft (Awock) came luring in the clouds.  
If you are a aircraft fanatic then this is your chance to get bragging rights having this Nft.  This is and will be the most rearest photo of this aircraft you will ever see. Because these ones are getting old and will be taking of duty soon.
